## Comandos AWS CLI Utilizados

- Criar stack:

aws cloudformation create-stack --stack-name StackS3EC2 --template-body file://C:/Users/anabe/Desktop/dio/template.yaml --parameters ParameterKey=InstanceType,ParameterValue=t2.micro --capabilities CAPABILITY_NAMED_IAM --region us-east-1


- Verificar status da stack:

aws cloudformation describe-stacks --stack-name StackS3EC2 --region us-east-1 --query "Stacks[0].StackStatus"


- Listar eventos da stack:

aws cloudformation describe-stack-events --stack-name StackS3EC2 --region us-east-1 --output table


- Listar instâncias EC2 criadas:

aws ec2 describe-instances --query "Reservations[*].Instances[*].[InstanceId,State.Name,KeyName,PublicIpAddress]" --output table


- Autorizar acesso SSH no Security Group:

aws ec2 authorize-security-group-ingress --group-id sg-04b7526516ce3ccee --protocol tcp --port 22 --cidr 0.0.0.0/0


- Conectar à instância EC2 via SSH:

ssh -i "C:/Users/anabe/Desktop/dio/minha-nova-chave.pem" ec2-user@<PublicIpAddress>
